<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>About - Natural Bodybuilding Shows</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { border-bottom: 2px solid #333; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    .nav { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .nav a { margin-right: 15px; text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc; }
    .nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .content { line-height: 1.6; }
    .federations { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .federation-card { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; }
    .federation-card h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #0066cc; }
    .federation-card h3 a { color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; }
    .federation-card h3 a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .federation-link { margin-top: 10px; }
    .federation-link a { background: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; }
    .federation-link a:hover { background: #0052a3; }
    .schedule-info { background: #e8f4fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #0066cc; margin: 20px 0; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .federations { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>About Natural Bodybuilding Shows</h1>
    <div class="nav">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>What This Site Does</h2>
    <p>All natural bodybuilding competition schedules in one convenient location! Instead of checking each organization's website separately, you can see all upcoming natural bodybuilding shows in one place.</p>

    <h2>For Competitors</h2>
    <p>Whether you're looking to compete in your first natural bodybuilding show or you're a seasoned competitor planning your competition season, this site helps you:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Find shows in your area or region</li>
      <li>Plan your competition calendar</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Natural Bodybuilding Federations</h2>
    <div class="federations">
      <div class="federation-card">
        <h3>WNBF (World Natural Bodybuilding Federation)</h3>
        <div class="federation-link">
          <a href="https://worldnaturalbb.com/" target="_blank">Visit WNBF Website →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="federation-card">
        <h3>OCB (Organization of Competitive Bodybuilders)</h3>
        <div class="federation-link">
          <a href="https://ocbonline.com/" target="_blank">Visit OCB Website →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="federation-card">
        <h3>Want to see a natural federation listed?</h3>
        <p>Know of another natural bodybuilding federation that should be included? Let us know!</p>
        <div class="federation-link">
          <a href="mailto:hi@natty.show?subject=New Natural Federation Suggestion">Suggest a Federation →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

